- cs.DM (Data Mining): The paper deals with large-scale datasets and proposes a method for feature selection. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a method for feature selection that can improve the explainability of machine-driven decisions. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Although not explicitly mentioned, the proposed method can be applied to high-dimensional image data, making this category a possibility.
